<p />
<h1><a name="About_this_Document"></a> About this Document </h1>
<!-- some useful variable definition <ul>
<li> Local UCL_HOST = ce
</li> <li> Local UCL_CWD  = ~
</li> <li> Set TWISTY_OPTS_DETAILED = mode="div" showlink="Show Detailed Output" hidelink="Hide" showimgleft="/twiki/pub/TWiki/TWikiDocGraphics/toggleopen-small.gif" hideimgleft="/twiki/pub/TWiki/TWikiDocGraphics/toggleclose-small.gif" remember="on" start="hide" 
</li></ul> 
<p />
-->
<p />
<img width="16" alt="hand" align="top" src="/twiki/pub/TWiki/TWikiDocGraphics/hand.gif" height="16" border="0" /> This document is for System Administrators. It starts with an introduction on Firewalls and how those terms are translated for OSG software. Then a brief description of services provided by a <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/GlossaryC#DefsComputeElement" class="twikiAnchorLink">Compute Element</a> and <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/GlossaryS#DefsStorageElement" class="twikiAnchorLink">Storage Element</a> will be given, followed by recommendations how to adjust the firewall for their correct operation. Servers have to worry about several ports while <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/Release3/InstallOSGClient" class="twikiLink">OSG Client</a> installations only have to worry about the <code>GLOBUS_TCP_PORT_RANGE</code>, <code>GLOBUS_TCP_SOURCE_RANGE</code> and the HTCondor ports (<code>LOWPORT</code>, <code>HIGHPORT</code>).
<p />
<p />
<!-- Some variables for the Firewall table - This version requires variables, does not work without changing the Web or Twiki preferences
Need this because double quotes used in Y in TWikiPreferences or ICON cause problems (replaced with single ones) <ul>
<li> Set ALTy = <img src='/twiki/pub/TWiki/TWikiDocGraphics/choice-yes.gif' alt='Y' title='Y' width='16' height='16' border='0' />    
</li></ul> 
<p />
Firewall variables: <ul>
<li> Set FIREWALL_HEADER = | <strong>Service Name</strong>  | <strong>Protocol</strong> | <strong>Port Number</strong> | <strong>Inbound</strong> | <strong>Outbound</strong> | <strong>Comment</strong>  |
</li> <li> Set FIREWALL_GRAM = | <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/GlossaryG#DefsGridResourceAllocationAndManagement" class="twikiAnchorLink">GRAM</a>  |  tcp  |  2119  |  <img src='/twiki/pub/TWiki/TWikiDocGraphics/choice-yes.gif' alt='Y' title='Y' width='16' height='16' border='0' />      | | |
</li> <li> Set FIREWALL_TPORT = | <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/GlossaryG#DefsGridResourceAllocationAndManagement" class="twikiAnchorLink">GRAM</a> callback  |  tcp  | <code>GLOBUS_TCP_PORT_RANGE</code> |  <img src='/twiki/pub/TWiki/TWikiDocGraphics/choice-yes.gif' alt='Y' title='Y' width='16' height='16' border='0' />      | | contiguous range of ports  |
</li> <li> Set FIREWALL_TSOURCE = | <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/GlossaryG#DefsGridResourceAllocationAndManagement" class="twikiAnchorLink">GRAM</a> callback  |  tcp  | <code>GLOBUS_TCP_SOURCE_RANGE</code> | |  <img src='/twiki/pub/TWiki/TWikiDocGraphics/choice-yes.gif' alt='Y' title='Y' width='16' height='16' border='0' />      | contiguous range of ports  |
</li> <li> Set FIREWALL_GRIDFTP = | <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/GlossaryG#DefsGridFTP" class="twikiAnchorLink">GridFTP</a>  |  tcp  | 2811 and <code>GLOBUS_TCP_SOURCE_RANGE</code> |  <img src='/twiki/pub/TWiki/TWikiDocGraphics/choice-yes.gif' alt='Y' title='Y' width='16' height='16' border='0' />      | | contiguous range of ports |
</li> <li> Set FIREWALL_SRM = | <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/GlossaryS#DefsSrm" class="twikiAnchorLink">Storage Resource Manager</a>  |  tcp  |  8080  |  <img src='/twiki/pub/TWiki/TWikiDocGraphics/choice-yes.gif' alt='Y' title='Y' width='16' height='16' border='0' />      | |  |
</li> <li> Set FIREWALL_SRM2 = | <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/GlossaryS#DefsSrm" class="twikiAnchorLink">Storage Resource Manager</a>  |  tcp  |  8443  |  <img src='/twiki/pub/TWiki/TWikiDocGraphics/choice-yes.gif' alt='Y' title='Y' width='16' height='16' border='0' />      | |  |
</li> <li> Set FIREWALL_GSISSH = | GSISSH  |  tcp/udp  |  22 or 2222  |  <img src='/twiki/pub/TWiki/TWikiDocGraphics/choice-yes.gif' alt='Y' title='Y' width='16' height='16' border='0' />      | | |
</li> <li> Set FIREWALL_MYPROXY = | MyProxy  |  tcp  |  7512  |  <img src='/twiki/pub/TWiki/TWikiDocGraphics/choice-yes.gif' alt='Y' title='Y' width='16' height='16' border='0' />      | | |
</li> <li> Set FIREWALL_GUMS = | <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/GlossaryG#DefsGridUserManagementSystem" class="twikiAnchorLink">GUMS</a>  |  tcp  |  8443  |  <img src='/twiki/pub/TWiki/TWikiDocGraphics/choice-yes.gif' alt='Y' title='Y' width='16' height='16' border='0' />      | | |
</li> <li> Set FIREWALL_VOMS = | <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/GlossaryV#DefsVoms" class="twikiAnchorLink">VOMS</a>  |  tcp  |  15001+  |  <img src='/twiki/pub/TWiki/TWikiDocGraphics/choice-yes.gif' alt='Y' title='Y' width='16' height='16' border='0' />      | | range of ports, increment by 1 for each VO supported  |
</li> <li> Set FIREWALL_VOMSADMIN = | <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/GlossaryV#DefsVomsAdmin" class="twikiAnchorLink">VOMS Admin</a>   |  tcp  |  8443  |  <img src='/twiki/pub/TWiki/TWikiDocGraphics/choice-yes.gif' alt='Y' title='Y' width='16' height='16' border='0' />      | | VOMS Admin (which runs within Tomcat) web interface, it must be available to VO administrators and users registering online |
</li> <li> Set FIREWALL_SQUID = | <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/GlossaryS#DefsSquid" class="twikiAnchorLink">Squid</a>  |  tcp  |  3128  |  <img src='/twiki/pub/TWiki/TWikiDocGraphics/choice-yes.gif' alt='Y' title='Y' width='16' height='16' border='0' />      | | |
</li> <li> Set FIREWALL_SQUIDMONITOR = | <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/GlossaryS#DefsSquidMonitor" class="twikiAnchorLink">Squid monitor</a>  |  udp  |  3401  |  <img src='/twiki/pub/TWiki/TWikiDocGraphics/choice-yes.gif' alt='Y' title='Y' width='16' height='16' border='0' />      | | |
</li> <li> Set FIREWALL_GRATIASERVICE = | <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/GlossaryV#DefsGratia" class="twikiAnchorLink">Gratia Service</a>   |  tcp  |  8443  |  <img src='/twiki/pub/TWiki/TWikiDocGraphics/choice-yes.gif' alt='Y' title='Y' width='16' height='16' border='0' />      | | Gratia Service (which runs within Tomcat) web interface. It must be available to all the probes reporting data, all servers receiving or sending replication data and the database |
</li> <li> Set FIREWALL_MYSQL = | <a href="http://www.mysql.com/" target="_top">MySQL</a> |  tcp  |  3306  |  <img src='/twiki/pub/TWiki/TWikiDocGraphics/choice-yes.gif' alt='Y' title='Y' width='16' height='16' border='0' />      | | 3306 is the default MySQL port. Can be configured to run on a different port. Can also communicate via a named pipe if the client is on the same host as the server |
</li> <li> Set FIREWALL_CONDOR =  | <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/GlossaryH#DefsHTCondor" class="twikiAnchorLink">HTCondor</a> port range  |  tcp  | <code>LOWPORT</code>, <code>HIGHPORT</code> |  <img src='/twiki/pub/TWiki/TWikiDocGraphics/choice-yes.gif' alt='Y' title='Y' width='16' height='16' border='0' />      | | contiguous range of ports  |
</li> <li> Set FIREWALL_CONDORCOLLECTOR =  | <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/GlossaryH#DefsHTCondor" class="twikiAnchorLink">HTCondor</a> collector  |  tcp  |  9618  |  <img src='/twiki/pub/TWiki/TWikiDocGraphics/choice-yes.gif' alt='Y' title='Y' width='16' height='16' border='0' />      | | HTCondor Collector (received ClassAds from resources and jobs) |
</li> <li> Set FIREWALL_CONDORSCHEDDSHARED =  | <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/GlossaryH#DefsHTCondor" class="twikiAnchorLink">HTCondor</a> collector  |  tcp  |  9615  |  <img src='/twiki/pub/TWiki/TWikiDocGraphics/choice-yes.gif' alt='Y' title='Y' width='16' height='16' border='0' />      | | HTCondor Schedd Shared Port|
</li> <li> Set FIREWALL_GWMSFRONTEND =  | <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/GlossaryG#DefsGlideinWMS" class="twikiAnchorLink">GlideinWMS Frontend</a>  |  tcp  |  9618 to 9660  |  <img src='/twiki/pub/TWiki/TWikiDocGraphics/choice-yes.gif' alt='Y' title='Y' width='16' height='16' border='0' />      | | HTCondor Collectors for the GlideinWMS Frontend (received ClassAds from resources and jobs) |
</li> <li> Set FIREWALL_HTCONDORCE = | <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/GlossaryH#DefsHtcondorCE" class="twikiAnchorLink">HTCondor-CE</a> ports | tcp | 9619 | <img src='/twiki/pub/TWiki/TWikiDocGraphics/choice-yes.gif' alt='Y' title='Y' width='16' height='16' border='0' />     | | Used to locate HTCondor-CE daemons |
</li> <li> Set FIREWALL_HTCONDORCESHARED = | <a href="/bin/view/Documentation/GlossaryH#DefsHtcondorCE" class="twikiAnchorLink">HTCondor-CE</a> shared daemon ports | tcp | 9620 | <img src='/twiki/pub/TWiki/TWikiDocGraphics/choice-yes.gif' alt='Y' title='Y' width='16' height='16' border='0' />     | | Used for aggregating ephemeral ports used by HTCondor into a single network port |
</li> <li> Set FIREWALL_ = 
</li></ul> 
<p /> <ul>
<li> Set FULLLIST = ,%lines%,
</li></ul> 
-->
